<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge.</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>We have just tried to contact you regarding your request to cancel your business insurance policy.</b></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">We would like to discuss what we can do to support you in this instance and explain what the options are for your business insurance.</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Please can you contact us on <b>01242 808740</b> so we can assist you with your request.</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Kind regards,</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!User.FirstName}</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Customer Accounts Team</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">T: 01242 808 740</font></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
